<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sp_instance"><sp_instance action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><class_name/><color>default</color><css>@media all {
  ul.nav.nav-pills.nav-sm > li {    
      overflow: hidden;
      text-overflow: ellipsis;
      white-space: pre;
  }
}
@media (min-width : 320px) and (max-width : 767px) {
  .nav li { 
    padding: 8px 0px;
  }
  .nav li > span > i { 
    padding-left: 5px;
  }
}
@media only screen and (min-width: 150px)  { ul.nav.nav-pills.nav-sm > li { max-width: 100px; } }
@media only screen and (min-width: 320px)  { ul.nav.nav-pills.nav-sm > li { max-width: 200px; } }
@media only screen and (min-width: 375px)  { ul.nav.nav-pills.nav-sm > li { max-width: 275px; } }
@media only screen and (min-width: 470px)  { ul.nav.nav-pills.nav-sm > li { max-width: 360px; } }
@media only screen and (min-width: 525px)  { ul.nav.nav-pills.nav-sm > li { max-width: 420px; } }
@media only screen and (min-width: 600px)  { ul.nav.nav-pills.nav-sm > li { max-width: 495px; } }
@media only screen and (min-width: 900px)  { ul.nav.nav-pills.nav-sm > li { max-width: 525px; } }
@media only screen and (min-width: 1200px)  { ul.nav.nav-pills.nav-sm > li { max-width: 650px; } }
@media (min-width : 320px) and (max-width : 767px) {
  ul.nav.nav-pills.nav-sm {
    margin-top: -5px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .nav-pills &gt; li + li {
    margin-left: 0px !important;
  }
}
